-up would only cause the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  to grow more skeptical about the effectiveness and capability of the government. The political expert pointed at rumors that after dismissing Minister Nurmahmudi, President Abdurrahman Wahid would also fire Finance Minister Prijadi Praptosuhardjo. The political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  created by President Abdurrahman Wahid himself may result in the failure of the nation's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery, he said. "For the sake of the nation's safety, it will be better for President Abdurrahman Wahid to declare his own resignation from the presidency," the political expert said. He called on what he termed "Gus Dur's whisperers" to stop conveying wrong information to the President in order to prevent him from making more mistakes that might lead to the misery of the whole nation. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020010709dx3h0016q\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
