\par\par \b \uc2  Sjahril warns of further interest rate increase. \b0\par\par\uc2 763 \uc2 words\par \uc2 24 March 2001\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  1 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  Governor Sjahril Sabirin said on Friday the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  would continue raising \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  if pressure on the rupiah persisted. \par \par \uc2  But Sjahril said he expected the government would soon reach an agreement with the International Monetary Fund to help reduce the pressure on the currency. \par \par \uc2  "The most important thing now is for the government to reach an agreement with the IMF. If this (agreement) can be reached it will be a very positive factor," he said following Friday prayers. \par \par \uc2  "But if (the agreement) cannot be reached, the rupiah will remain under strong pressure," he said, adding that if the pressure continued the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  inevitably would raise \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  to defend the embattled local unit. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril said the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  also would continue to intervene in the currency market by selling its dollar \b \highlight22\uc2 reserves\b0 \highlight\uc2  to help stabilize the rupiah. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  raised the benchmark interest rate of its one-month SBI promissory note to 15.24 percent during the weekly market auction on Wednesday, up from 14.94 percent the previous week. \par \par \uc2  Some observers are concerned the increase in the benchmark interest rate could create new trouble for the fragile domestic banking industry and threaten the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Bankers and analysts have said a further increase in \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  could cause banks to suffer negative spread. \par \par \uc2  The rising \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  also could increase the burden on the already strained state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , which must cover the interest of the government's bank recapitalization bonds. Part of the interest of these bonds is linked to the SBI rate. \par \par \uc2  The rupiah dropped to a 30-month low of Rp 11,500 against the US dollar earlier this month, the result of a combination of strong corporate dollar demand, domestic political and security \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  and a standoff between the government and the IMF. \par \par \uc2  But the rupiah has stabilized somewhat this week as a result of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 's decision to intervene in the market and increase \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  The rupiah closed slightly higher on Friday at Rp 10,385 to the dollar from Rp 10,390 on Thursday. Dealers said the rupiah was helped by reports that the Indonesian Bank Restructuring Agency (IBRA) had begun to convert its dollars into rupiah. \par \par \uc2  Minister of Finance Prijadi Praptosuhardjo said on Thursday IBRA sold about $17 million last week, adding that the agency would continue to sell its dollars. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril welcomed the move by IBRA, but he also said a stable political situation was crucial for a stronger rupiah. \par \par \uc2  Narrowing differences \par \par \uc2  Separately, Coordinating Minister for the \b \highlight22\uc2 Economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  Rizal Ramli said on Friday the government expected to be able to reach a new agreement with the IMF soon, as the two parties were continuing to iron out their differences. \par \par \uc2  "Our differences have been narrowing," Rizal said following a ceremony to install the new head of the State Logistics Agency, Widjanarko Puspoyo. But he declined to say when the government would reach a deal with the IMF. \par \par \uc2  The IMF pledged a total of $5 billion to help finance the country's three-year \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform program, and has so far disbursed about $1 billion of this amount. \par \par \uc2  Late last year, the IMF delayed the disbursement of the third $400 million tranche because of what it saw as the government's wavering on key \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reforms. The IMF specifically cited the delay in the sale of the government's stakes in Bank Central Asia (BCA) and Bank Niaga, and its concern with the government-proposed amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law and the new \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  decentralization \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  The delay in the delivery of the IMF tranche has prompted other multilateral institutions, including the World Bank and the Asian Development Bank, to cut their aid to Indonesia. \par \par \uc2  Expectations of a new agreement with the IMF increased when the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  recently approved the government's plan to divest its ownership in BCA and Bank Niaga. \par \par \uc2  The government also has agreed to the IMF's demand to form a panel of international experts to review the proposed amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law. \par \par \uc2  Rizal said the former head of the National Development Planning Board, Boediono, and banking expert Sutan Remy Sjahdeini had been named to represent the government on the panel. And he said former \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  governors from New Zealand and Chile would be included on the panel as representatives of the IMF. \par \par \uc2  Rizal also said a small IMF technical team had arrived in Jakarta and was discussing \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  decentralization with the Ministry of Finance. (rei) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010712dx3o004g0\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
