\par\par \b \uc2  News of impending IMF visit fails to bring cheer to rupiah. \b0\par\par\uc2 790 \uc2 words\par \uc2 7 April 2001\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  1 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): The rupiah dropped again on Friday despite news that the International Monetary Fund (IMF) mission would visit Jakarta on Wednesday. \par \par \uc2  The local currency, which fell to its low of Rp 10,940 against the U.S. dollar in early trade, eased slightly to close at Rp 10,875, following intervention by \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  (BI). \par \par \uc2  Despite the slight gain, the Indonesian unit was, however, still lower when compared with its level of Rp 10,740 in late trading on Thursday. \par \par \uc2  Currency analyst Farial Anwar said that the further fall of the rupiah was partly due to the fall in other regional currencies, which have been weakening against the dollar over the past few days. \par \par \uc2  Farial said that the internal factors which had been putting pressure on the rupiah were still basically the same: political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  and negative developments on the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  front. \par \par \uc2  He said that the rupiah could soon move through the new Rp 11,000 resistance level. \par \par \uc2  Farial said that on the political side, worsening relations between embattled President Abdurrahman Wahid and his opponents had been creating jitters in the currency market, particularly with the latest reports of Abdurrahman's supporters planning a holy war. \par \par \uc2  Media reports saying that the President doubted the competence of Vice President Megawati Soekarnoputri to become President also played a part in the loss of confidence in the local currency. \par \par \uc2  Farial said that on the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  side, reports that the 2001 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  could be greater than projected had also undermined confidence. \par \par \uc2  Coordinating Minister for the \b \highlight22\uc2 Economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  Rizal Ramli said this week that the \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  could exceed 5 percent of gross domestic product (GDP) compared with the original estimate of 3.7 percent of GDP, unless measures were taken immediately. \par \par \uc2  Farial said fears of a further slide in the rupiah had prompted corporations to purchase dollars, including those for the purpose of debt repayment. \par \par \uc2  "But there are also those holding huge cash sums who are purchasing dollars in a flight toward hard currency," he said, pointing out that some people perceive the dollar as a safer currency, while investment in the rupiah is haunted by the specter of inflation, higher \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2 , and depreciation. \par \par \uc2  It is expected that the IMF would send a mission to Jakarta on Wednesday to review the possibility of the Fund to disburse the latest, but currently stalled, US$400 million loan tranche to Indonesia. \par \par \uc2  "The mission should start work next Wednesday...all conditions for the mission (to visit) have been met," IMF Indonesia representative John Dodsworth told Reuters. \par \par \uc2  "But the market has already discounted this," Farial said. \par \par \uc2  Dodsworth said earlier this week that the IMF mission would make the visit early next week, after a panel of international and domestic experts have completed the review of the government-proposed amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law. \par \par \uc2  Earlier in the day, BI Governor Sjahril Sabirin stated that he expected the rupiah to appreciate with the visit of the IMF mission. \par \par \uc2  "Let's hope the IMF team can reach agreement with the government ... this will help the rupiah," Sjahril said. \par \par \uc2  He added that if the rupiah appreciated, there would be room for the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  to allow the interest rate of its SBI promissory notes to decline. \par \par \uc2  The SBI interest rate has been increasing during recent weeks, raising concern that it would create trouble for some banks. \par \par \uc2  It remains unclear, however, whether the IMF mission will be able to reach agreement with the government over key \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform issues. The remaining important issues include slow progress in corporate debt restructuring and concern over the controversial amendments to the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  The IMF postponed disbursement of the next tranche of its loan to the country in December last year due to signs of the government wavering in its key \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform program, including delay in the divestment of government ownership in Bank Central Asia and Bank Niaga, and concern over the poor implementation of \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  decentralization \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law. \par \par \uc2  But the legislature has recently approved the bank divestment plan, and the government has issued a decree banning provincial and district administrations from borrowing for the time being. \par \par \uc2  The delay in the disbursement of the IMF loan also prompted other international lenders to put on hold their assistance to Indonesia, and creditors threatened to cancel the restructuring of the country's sovereign debt. \par \par \uc2  The panel of experts is expected to complete the review of the proposed amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law on Sunday, and to report to the government. \par \par \uc2  The IMF has expressed concern that the proposed amendment of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law would jeopardize the independence of BI. (rei) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010712dx47004gj\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
