\par\par \b \uc2  Muddling through  \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty \highlight\uc2 . \b0\par\par\uc2 711 \uc2 words\par \uc2 2 May 2001\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  4 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  The big question arising, now that the political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  has escalated to the probability of a change in government, is how the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  will muddle through the transition period. \par \par \uc2  How the government of President Abdurrahman Wahid, further demoralized by the second memorandum of censure from the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 , will be able to manage the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  amid the sharply eroded market confidence. How reform measures, badly needed to maintain the budding \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery, can still proceed under a government whose credibility and popularity are now at their nadir. \par \par \uc2  Such issues would not be so worrisome in most other countries where the head of government can change at any time without causing serious damage to the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 . This is because most governments are supported by a strong system of bureaucracy and similarly well-established institutions in the other branches of the government - the judiciary and legislature. \par \par \uc2  But the current situation that is leading toward a seemingly unavoidable change of government could be quite tumultuous in Indonesia, where the institutions in all branches of the government are still in the process of adjusting from an authoritarian to democratic system. \par \par \uc2  What makes this process even more complex and potentially explosive is the four year old \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis that is threatening to lead the government into bankruptcy and leave the whole \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in tatters. \par \par \uc2  This is the kind of situation that urgently calls upon the President and the House, despite their differences, to demonstrate strong spirit of statesmanship by continuing good cooperation in leading the nation and country through the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  First of all, Abdurrahman needs to order his Cabinet, notably the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  team, to continue their responsibilities as normal and implement the reform agenda according to schedule, especially the debt and corporate restructuring programs, which are pivotal to sustaining the nascent recovery. \par \par \uc2  Vice President Megawati Soekarnoputri, who has been assigned by the President to lead Cabinet meetings, is required to work even harder to ensure that the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  can negotiate the transition period without further damage being inflicted upon the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  fundamentals. As the strongest candidate positioned to take over from Abdurrahman, when his replacement finally becomes unavoidable, Megawati should realize that the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  would make or break her leadership. \par \par \uc2  Even though it is now virtually impossible to improve market confidence amid the political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 , \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  consistency during the transition period would help maintain whatever little confidence remains and make it much easier to accelerate the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery once the political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  is resolved. \par \par \uc2  The House's role is no less crucial in helping prevent the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  from deteriorating, because many reform measures require its approval. \par \par \uc2  The most urgent priorities now are quick deliberation of the proposed amendments to the 2001 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law. Completion of these programs would pave the way for a new agreement with the International Monetary Fund and expedite the release of its third US$400 million loan tranche, suspended since December. \par \par \uc2  A new accord with the IMF, which amounts to an internationally-endorsed \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  reform agenda, would kick-start the process of regaining market confidence and the trust of foreign creditors in the country. \par \par \uc2  Without market confidence the rupiah exchange rate against the American dollar, already as low as its levels reached during the peak of the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis in 1998, will continue to weaken and consequently inflate the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  costs of fuel \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidies\b0 \highlight\uc2  and foreign debt servicing. \par \par \uc2  Further rupiah depreciation will also force the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  to continue raising \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  in a bid to curb import inflationary pressures. This, in turn, will increase the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  costs of domestic debt (bond) servicing, stifle \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  activities and heighten the risk of bad debts for banks. Just look at how the composite price index of the Jakarta Stock Exchange, a main barometer of the real sector, which had risen to as high as 510 early last year, has now plunged again to less than 360 points. \par \par \uc2  It is, therefore, most imperative that the President and the House immediately put their enmity aside and start setting deadlines for finalizing amendments to the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  and \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  laws and consolidating a new reform agenda. We cannot afford to waste any more time while the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  continues to bleed. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010712dx52005f7\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
